This paper is about conversational systems and natural language processing, which are typically covered in the Computer Science sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The paper also proposes a new neural network architecture, which falls under the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves experimentation and evaluation of the proposed method, which could fall under the sub-categories of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) and Sound (cs.SD).
